title: Sonia wins PP-124 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate, Sonia has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-124, Toba Tek Singh-VI by securing 62,062 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League (N) candidate, Syed Qutab Ali Shah, who bagged 55,930 votes.
The votersâ€™ turnout remained 59.27%.
